{
  "stem": "150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I take it home, and it's written by a guy who was very much involved in illegal arms smuggling to the Haganah, to the Jewish Resistance, to the Jewish underground army under the British, because the Jewish soldiers, naturally, were stealing whatever weapons they could get and sending them illegally to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all kinds of very brave and very sharp things were being done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, you shipped guns like tractors, and pianos were really machine guns, and God knows what else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, I read the book, and it's very fascinating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I come across a chapter entitled 'Magenta,' which is the name of the place we were at.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it says the main center of arms packing and trans shipping activity in Italy was a little agricultural settlement called Magenta.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Naturally, they didn't want any kids around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had nothing against us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They just didn't want any kids hanging around while they were doing this kind of stuff where everybody could get busted by the British any minute.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I forgave them many years later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I felt much better about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I stayed on in Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, who was also asking everybody she met, you know, have you seen my kid?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Have you seen my husband?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where was she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was left for dead with typhus, and when the Russians came they found all those bodies lying around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of them were still alive, so they put her-- and her sister, as a matter of fact, was in the same camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her sister survived because her little girl was kept by Gentiles in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If she had had a little girl, it would also be bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
